    "It exhibits an improvement of 8.83% compared to the average pooling's average optimal value performance.",
    "• The T-Max-Avg method can further enhance the accuracy of the Avg-TopK approach on the CIFAR-10 dataset.",
    "With a pooling size of 2, K value of 1, and T equal to 0.7, it achieves a performance improvement of 1.4% compared to the average top-K approach and a performance improvement of 1.93% compared to the average maximal pooling approach.",
